Module project

Package game

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Behaviour
    A factory for creating actions.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Application
    The main class for the zombie apocalypse game.
    AttackAction
    Special Action for attacking other Actors.
    AttackBehaviour
    A class that generates an AttackAction if the current Actor is standing next to an Actor that they can attack.
    Corpse
    StationaryItem that represents a corpse.
    CraftAction
    An Action that takes an instance of a parent Item and a child Item and performs the action of removing the parent Item and adding the child Item to the game, depending on whether it was called on an Item on the Map or in an Actor's inventory.
    Crop
    A class that represents Crop, a type of Ground that can be interacted with by Farmers and other Actors to yield Food, a PortableItem that has beneficial effects to Human Actors.
    Dirt
    A class that represents bare dirt.
    EatFoodAction
    An Action that heals the Actor that calls this method and removes the consumed Food from the map or Actor inventory.
    Farmer
    A special Human that has access to FarmingBehaviour that allows the Farmer to interact with Crop tiles.
    FarmingBehaviour
    A class that figures out what farming Action a Farmer can perform on a given turn, depending on circumstances.
    Fence
    An impenetrable barrier.
    FertiliseAction
    An action that fertilises a Crop at a given location.
    FollowBehaviour
    A class that figures out a MoveAction that will move the actor one step closer to a target Actor.
    Food
    A special type of PortableItem that can be consumed by Actors to restore HP.
    HarvestAction
    Action that harvests the Crop at a given Location.
    Human
    Class representing an ordinary human.
    HumanPunch
    A Human specific punch attack.
    HuntActorBehaviour
    Returns a MoveAction that will take the Actor closer to the nearest instance of an Actor class.
    HuntBehaviour
    An abstract class that brings the caller Actor one square closer to an instance of anything.
    HuntGroundBehaviour
    Returns a MoveAction that will take the Actor closer to the nearest instance of a Ground class This uses a breadth-first search algorithm and is based on code written for the FIT2099 assignment in S2 2019 by Spike.
    HuntItemBehaviour
    Returns a MoveAction that will take the Actor closer to the nearest instance of an Item class.
    InfectedCorpse
    Special type of Corpse that reanimates as a Zombie 5-10 turns after creation.
    Plank
    A primitive weapon.
    Player
    Class representing the Player.
    PortableItem
    Base class for any item that can be picked up and dropped.
    SowAction
    Action that changes the Ground at the target Location to Crop.
    StationaryItem
    Base class for any item that can't be picked up and dropped.
    Tree
    A tree that starts as a sapling and grows into a large tree.
    WanderBehaviour
    Allows an Actor to wander around at random.
    Zombie
    A Zombie.
    ZombieActor
    Base class for Actors in the Zombie World
    ZombieArm
    A zombie arm weapon.
    ZombieBite
    A Zombie specific bite attack.
    ZombieClub
    A zombie club weapon.
    ZombieLeg
    A zombie leg weapon.
    ZombieMace
    A zombie mace weapon.
    ZombiePunch
    A Zombie specific punch attack.
